data.description: Featuring a NEW (September 2023) architectural shingle ROOF, and NEW custom seamless gutter system. Nestled in Ponte Vedra Beach's gated enclave community of ''Belvedere Place'' this elegant and welcoming home is filled with abundant natural light and painted in a peaceful coastal palette. You'll be greeted with a courtyard entry paver driveway, three car garage, and custom travertine entry patio.  Inside features four large bedrooms & four full baths, along with an updated kitchen, family room, separate formal living and dining rooms, dedicated office PLUS a secluded study/library w/ built in shelving, pocket doors, & ''Versailles'' design stone floors. The large primary suite and quiet office are accentuated with gorgeous custom French Oak wood flooring. The roomy and private primary suite has tray ceiling, automatic blinds, ceiling fan and a newly remodeled in 2023, beautifully tiled ensuite bathroom w/zero entry shower, whirlpool style jetted tub, double vanities with marble countertops, Kohler Fixtures, plus two walk-in closets with built in shelving. There is plenty of room for guests upstairs highlighted with a split suite three bedroom and two bath layout. See documents for the detailed floor plan. The heart of this home is the Cook's Kitchen, which has a granite slab island with second sink.  Ideal for daily meal prep or Holiday entertainment the kitchen features two JennAire ovens, a microwave, Kitchen Aide French Drawer style stainless refrigerator and an induction cooktop with pro-style vent hood, conveniently overlooking the family room w/ custom built-ins & entertainment center, gas fireplace, tray ceiling and automatic blinds. Eat in breakfast area adjoins the kitchen with a view of the covered lanai leading out to the large screened pavered patio, where it's easy to relax and enjoy nature and your fenced backyard.  The HVAC system has multiple zones with new (2023) state of the art individual Honeywell programmable thermostats allowing for efficient and cost-effective conditioning and cooling. Wi-Fi controlled Rainbird irrigation system, Rinnai tankless gas water heater, and new NEST smoke detectors add to the thoughtful list of recent updates. Just moments away from the beach, shopping, medical offices, golf courses, many restaurants, and the local library.
